{
  "title": "Fast Fried Portuguese Style Peanut Brittle Fritters",
  "description": "Quick, earthy, and bouncy Portuguese-style fritters featuring peanut brittle and a miso-marinate, easy to make in a cazuela. Perfect as a snack or dessert.",
  "cuisine": "Portuguese",
  "diet": null,
