  "instructions": [
    "In a large mixing bowl, whisk together the flour, baking powder, and a pinch of salt.",
    "Add the crushed peanut brittle, egg replacer, and granulated sugar to the dry ingredients and mix until well combined.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together the miso paste, water, miso broth, and a pinch of black pepper.",
    "Add the miso mixture to the dry ingredients and mix until a dough forms.",
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a cazuela over medium-high heat until it reaches 350°F.",
    "Using a spoon, drop the dough into the hot oil, making sure not to overcrowd the cazuela.",
    "Fry the fritters for 2-3 minutes on each side, or until golden brown and crispy."
  ],
